column2: SELECT p.objId, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.expAB_r, p.dered_u as u, p.dered_g as g, p.dered_r as r, p.dered_i as i, s.z, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.g as mag, n.sersic_n, Amplitude_Ha_# as ampHa, e.Amplitude_Hb_# as ampHb, e.Amplitude_Hb_#_Err as amphb, e.Flux_Ha_# as fluxHa, Flux_Hb_# as fluxHb FROM galaxy AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN nsatlas AS n ON n.mjd = s.mjd and n.fiberID = s.fiberID and n.plate = s.plate JOIN emissionLinesPort as e ON e.plate = n.plate and e.fiberID = n.fiberID WHERE p.petror9#_r > # and p.ra between # and # and s.z between # and .# and p.g < #
